{
  "texts": [
    "Fig. 2 A timeline of some representative LLM datasets.",
    "Orange represents pre-training corpora, yellow represents instruction fine-tuning datasets, green represents preference datasets, and pink represents evaluation datasets models, resulting in well-performing general conversational models or domain-specific models.",
    "The widespread adoption of Reinforcement Learning from Human Feedback (RLHF) and the refinement of LLM evaluations further optimize the performance of LLMs.",
    "The immense potential demonstrated by LLMs can be attributed, in part, to the datasets used for training and testing.",
    "As the saying goes, \"You can't make a silk purse out of a sow's ear.\""
  ]
}